{"id":672,"type":4,"name":"Quake 4","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/2d/ea/672_3Qq81.jpg","rating":{"total":33,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":3,"6":4,"7":14,"8":9,"9":2,"10":0},"score":7},"summary":"　　《QUAKE 4》将会是系列中第一款让你扮演真正有名字的主角的游戏。他是一名太空舰队队员，名叫Matthew Kane，是突击队中的精锐，有着神秘的过去。Kane被派遣到Rhino 小队中，这个小组和多个小组一起被派进攻strogg 的故乡——Stroggos行星。实际上，《QUAKE 4》是《QUAKE 2》的后续之作。在《QUAKE 2》中，主人公是一个无名的太空船员，他的任务是击退恶心的strogg，这些strogg为捕捉到的生物装上机械部分来改进他们的身体，然后为他们植入神经控制将他们转变为没有头脑的奴隶。游戏的巅峰战斗发生在Stroggos行星上，主人公来到这个行星，杀掉了stogg的首领“makron”，可惜这个致命的打击并没有结束这场斗争。现在地球派遣了像Rhino 小队这样的太空舰队进攻strogg行星，以永久地解除整个宇宙受到的威胁。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>雷神之锤4</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/23616\">id Software</a>、<a href=\"/person/32572\">Raven Software</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>XBOX360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Mac OS X</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>FPS</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>id Tech 4</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>多人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>Windows 2005-10-18</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">发行日期: </span>Mac OS X 2006-3-24</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">发行日期: </span>XBOX360 2005-11-8</li><li><span>制作公司: </span>Raven Software</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">制作公司: </span>id Software</li><li><span>发行公司: </span>Activison</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">发行公司: </span>Bethesda Softworks</li>","collection":{"wish":5,"collect":46,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":4},{"name":"id","count":2},{"name":"主角改造计划","count":2},{"name":"雷神之锤","count":1},{"name":"FPS","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":23616,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8a/8a/23616_prsn_nA7HE.jpg","name":"id Software","desc":"开发"},{"id":32572,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/de/f0/32572_prsn_EByEB.jpg","name":"乌鸦软件","desc":"开发"}],"relations":[{"id":49297,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a9/58/49297_O3Zg3.jpg","title":"Quake II","type":"前传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/49297"},{"id":185071,"image":"//lain.bgm